Anyone with AGI less than 75 is penalized on their AC as a result.  You weren't really seeing a huge &quot;jump&quot; in your AC, you were merely seeing the results of having your Agi in above the &quot;penalty-line.&quot;<br>
<br>
Sorry to burst the bubble but there's no &quot;amazing&quot; jumps at 100, 120, etc...  Agi boosts on items do add to your AC slightly.  I think +1Agi = +1AC, but I haven't played around with it lately.<br>
<br>
